{"tid":1394454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[3/8旺角行動建議]一定要現場開會先","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:29:53.000Z","uid":108757,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87244948a53b09c91939c153899dfeda666b013f","tid":1394454,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"唔該大家每次行動之前，現場搵個地方同在場手足開會先，好似612同71咁傾好晒<br />\n1. 行動<span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span><br />\n2. 行動手段<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: green;\">撤退時間+撤退路線</span><br />\n4. 哨兵地點<br />\n跟住先跟住計畫，各有各做。我相信可以增加成效。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「夫兵形象水，水之行避高而趨下，兵之形避實而擊虛；水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故<span style=\"color: green;\">兵無常勢，水無常形。</span>」<br />\n<br />\nBe water!!"},{"pid":"23e5ecf066f82914c420093c86e6f7a622900259","tid":1394454,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48d7ff2888a98fdb3f68c3f00d31fe0c8cd86d0","tid":1394454,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd407447205604b166e07e1d389fe22919ca541c","tid":1394454,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"89666ccdee508ca560cb9f255f34094b88badc9e","tid":1394454,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"5/8 齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd490ff005490ea030096b99edfa46c1ed0c1b5","tid":1394454,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"5/8 齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34a40ca845a14fb781f